22
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:50,970
There's a ton of things that we can buy

23
00:00:50,970 --> 00:00:52,460
with our organization's money.

24
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:54,520
We want to make sure
we're doing it responsibly

25
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:57,480
and that we're going to get
the best bang for our buck.

26
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:00,380
Service Financial Management
is all of those backend things

27
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:01,650
that the accountants are going to do

28
00:01:01,650 --> 00:01:03,380
and the business analysts are going to do

29
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:05,885
to ensure that our company
remains financially solvent

30
00:01:05,885 --> 00:01:08,160
and that we're able to continue operating

31
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,070
because we have money
to pay our employees,

32
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:12,310
pay for our services,
pay for our contract,

33
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,763
and keep the business afloat.

